    "name": "Mirage Noir",
    "steam_appid": 3048330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras/474ee282c1939dc6595cb4cabfa24b0d.avif?t=1770342517\" width=616 height=126 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>Mirage Noir </strong>is a detective romance visual novel where every lead could bring you closer to love—or straight into a killer’s hands.</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When Yunie graduated from college, she believed she had her whole life ahead of her. Returning to her hometown with a shiny new dream job, it seemed like nothing could stand in her way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, two years later, not much has changed. She hasn't made any new friends, isn't allowed to investigate anything worthwhile, and feels like she's stuck in mud, moving in place. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So when an unexpected opportunity arises, she doesn't hesitate to take it. The case is a weird one, but it introduces her to an eccentric team of people she immediately connects with, and she decides that no matter what, she won't regret getting involved. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if it means crossing paths with a serial killer. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Full game coming in 2026! The demo covers the entirety of the prologue and contains 3-5 hours of content.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras/b7e4c46d427792199d00b7cfe3ebc943.avif?t=1770342517\" width=616 height=126 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >200,000+ words (~50,000 word demo that covers the entirety of the prologue) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 character routes that can be played in any order </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 &quot;truth&quot; routes that are unlocked once all 4 character routes are cleared. You can also choose your romantic partner during these and get character-specific scenes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minigames, including point-and-click investigations and real time segments. You will be allowed to skip some of them if they're not enjoyable </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collectable Side Stories </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Changeable MC name </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras/eb9af8235b8bb72347d02bfa8f2d40e0.avif?t=1770342517\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to it being a visual novel, the game also has several different minigames. Most of them can be toggled on/off, and those that can't will have a story mode for players who'd prefer to focus on the plot instead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras/89e134cc45ddfdf86c36e4b9b99e83d1.avif?t=1770342517\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras_big/89e134cc45ddfdf86c36e4b9b99e83d1.avif?t=1770342517 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>(Multiscreen gameplay, evidence collecting, deduction segments, point-and-click investigations, and more!)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras/3ad262102e390ab77b0360ca2669d7a3.avif?t=1770342517\" width=800 height=108 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>If you'd like to support us, please consider backing us on Kickstarter! We are trying to fund voice acting. The link can be found in the sidebar.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras/1abab6324bb862d367daf524761fd727.avif?t=1770342517\" width=800 height=163 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras/a8a3696563666ae3a1e0f2a92cbfd368.avif?t=1770342517\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras_big/a8a3696563666ae3a1e0f2a92cbfd368.avif?t=1770342517 width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras/e686dee5afd70770ecd91ae20f0239ce.avif?t=1770342517\" width=616 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mirage Noir is told through the point of view of a detective and focuses on the cases that happen around her as well as the four boys she meets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras/a14452cad7532e50949a662e4305e3df.avif?t=1770342517\" width=616 height=449 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras/089d635183d79148770c3ce63bddda81.avif?t=1770342517\" width=616 height=449 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras/b1fe88eaa362ef70128cf3a67dedd08e.avif?t=1770342517\" width=616 height=449 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras/39d7ed8e8d259ec35589bdab2a487272.avif?t=1770342517\" width=616 height=449 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048330/extras/1a30608ac5e7c8c69f06ec87eb3272f4.avif?t=1770342517\" width=616 height=449 /></span></p>",
